# registeredNibsByIdentifier

**Instance Property**

The dictionary of all registered nib files for view-based table view identifiers.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var registeredNibsByIdentifier: [NSUserInterfaceItemIdentifier : NSNib]? { get }
```

## Discussion

Each key in the dictionary is the identifier string (given by [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSUserInterfaceItemIdentifier]) used to register the nib file in the [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSTableView/register(_:forIdentifier:)] method. The value of each key is the corresponding [doc://com.apple.appkit/documentation/AppKit/NSNib] object.



## NSView-Based Table Nib File Registration

- **register(_:forIdentifier:)**: Registers a NIB for the specified identifier, so that view-based table views can use it to instantiate views.
